'''Jason Brian Carter''' ([[23 September|September 23]], [[1960]]) voiced [[Glorfindel]] in ''[[EA's The Battle for Middle-earth II]]'' and its expansion, ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Battle for Middle-earth II: The Rise of the Witch-king|The Rise of the Witch-king]]''. 

He auditioned for the role of [[Aragorn]] in [[The Lord of the Rings (film series)|''The Lord of the Rings'' (film series)]]. Carter was stated as trying out for the role but was not what the casting crew was looking for.
